headline: 3 Top Dividend Stocks You Shouldn't Hesitate to Buy This February
summary: Dividend stocks can be terrific investments.  The best ones provide investors with passive income and upside potential.  Over the last 50 years, dividend stocks have outperformed non-payers by more than 2-to-1, according to data from Hartford Funds and Ned Davis Research.
